document_api_meta.title: Get Inbound Order
document_api_meta.env_desc: This API is used to retrieve the inbound order details including the planned inbound detail, actual inbound detail and inbound status, etc.

request_header_param.name: x-tts-access-token
request_header_param.desc: The seller access_token value from [Get Access Token](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a3292b0f40314a92d75#Get%20Access%20Token%20API), when user_type = 0. Follow this [guide](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/678e3a344ddec3030b238fa0) to get seller access_token.

request_query_param.name: app_key
request_query_param.desc: Every single app will have a unique key. Please use the specific key assigned to your app.

request_query_param.name: sign
request_query_param.desc: Signature generated by gen algorithm. When you send API requests to TTS, you must sign them so that TTS can identify the senders.

request_query_param.name: timestamp
request_query_param.desc: Unix timestamp GMT (UTC+00:00). This timestamp is used across all API requests. Developers can use this convert to local time.

request_query_param.name: ids
request_query_param.desc:
A list of inbound order IDs needs to be queried. The API will return the inbound order information for these IDs.
Note: The inbound ID consists of a series of numbers without the "IBR" prefix.
You can get the value in `data.inbound_order_id` in [Inbound FBT order status change](6708f866a88d1103246fed6a) webhook or in `data.inventory_records.order.id` in the response of [Search FBT Inventory Record](670d584ba83c5f030f3071e4).

request_query_param.name: shop_cipher
request_query_param.desc:
Use this property to pass shop information in requesting the API. Failure in passing the correct value when requesting the API for cross-border shops will return incorrect response. 
Get by API [Get Authorization Shop](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9?external_id=6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9)

response_param.name: code
response_param.desc: The success or failure status code returned in API response.

response_param.name: message
response_param.desc: The success or failure messages returned in API response. Reasons of failure will be described in the message.

response_param.name: request_id
response_param.desc: Request log

response_param.name: data
response_param.desc: Specific return information

response_param.name: ^inbound_orders
response_param.desc: A list of inbound order detail information.

response_param.name: ^^id
response_param.desc: The identifier for inbound order generated in Fillfilled by TikTok system.

response_param.name: ^^type
response_param.desc:
The inbound order type.
Possible values:
- REPLENISHMENT

response_param.name: ^^merchant
response_param.desc: Merchant information.

response_param.name: ^^^id
response_param.desc: The identifier of the merchant in Fulfilled by TikTok system.

response_param.name: ^^^name
response_param.desc: The merchant name.

response_param.name: ^^create_time
response_param.desc: The time when the inbound order created. Unix timestamp in seconds.

response_param.name: ^^ship_time
response_param.desc: The time when the inbound order shipped. Unix timestamp in seconds.

response_param.name: ^^expect_arrive_time
response_param.desc: The expected arrival time provided by merchant. Unix timestamp in seconds.

response_param.name: ^^actual_arrive_time
response_param.desc: The actual arrival time. Unix timestamp in seconds.

response_param.name: ^^warehouse
response_param.desc: The warehouse information.

response_param.name: ^^^fbt_warehouse_id
response_param.desc: The Identifier for warehouse generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system.

response_param.name: ^^^warehouse_ids
response_param.desc: The identifier for warehouse generated by TikTok Shop system, will have the relationship with `fbt_warehouse_id`.

response_param.name: ^^^name
response_param.desc: The Fulfilled by TikTok warehouse name.

response_param.name: ^^^type
response_param.desc:
The Fullfilled by TikTok  warehouse type.  
Possible values:
- PLATFORM_WAREHOUSE

response_param.name: ^^planned_goods
response_param.desc: A list of planned goods details in the inbound order.

response_param.name: ^^^id
response_param.desc: The identifier for goods generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system.

response_param.name: ^^^reference_code
response_param.desc: The identifier for goods defined by merchant.

response_param.name: ^^^name
response_param.desc: The Fulfilled by TikTok goods name.

response_param.name: ^^^quantity
response_param.desc: The planned goods quantity.

response_param.name: ^^^sku_ids
response_param.desc: The identifier for Stock Keeping Unit (SKU) generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system.

response_param.name: ^^received_batches
response_param.desc: A list of actual received inbound order batch details.

response_param.name: ^^^id
response_param.desc: The identifier for inbound put away batch.

response_param.name: ^^^goods_id
response_param.desc: The identifier for goods generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system.

response_param.name: ^^^normal_quantity
response_param.desc: The quantity of normal goods in the inbound order batch.

response_param.name: ^^^defective_quantity
response_param.desc: The quantity of defective goods in the inbound order batch.

response_param.name: ^^^product_ids
response_param.desc: A list of product identifiers generated by TikTok Shop, which will be empty if the current goods do not match any product.

response_param.name: ^^^sku_ids
response_param.desc: A list of SKU (Stock Keeping Unit) identifiers generated by TikTok Shop, which will be empty if the current goods do not match any SKU.

response_param.name: ^^^total_quantity
response_param.desc: The total number of units received by the Fulfilled by TikTok warehouse in the inbound order batch, which is the sum of `normal_quantity` and `defective_quantity`.

response_param.name: ^^order_operation_logs
response_param.desc: A list of inbound order operation history.

response_param.name: ^^^operate_time
response_param.desc: The time when the inbound order is processed by the merchant or warehouses, represented as a Unix timestamp in seconds.

response_param.name: ^^^order_status
response_param.desc:
The order status in Fulfilled by TikTok warehouse.
Possible values:
- WORKING
- READY_TO_SHIP
- TO_BE_RECEIVED
- ARRIVED_HUB
- INTERNAL_TRANSFER
- RECEIVING
- PARTIALLY_RECEIVED
- RECEIVED
- CANCELLED
- DELIVERED

response_param.name: ^^carriers
response_param.desc: A list of carrier information.

response_param.name: ^^^carrier_name
response_param.desc: The carrier name.

response_param.name: ^^^tracking_number
response_param.desc: The tracking number for the current inbound shipment with the carrier.
